headline: Borderlands® 4 Coming to Nintendo Switch™ 2 on October 3
summary: NEW YORK, July 31, 2025--Today, 2K and Gearbox Software announced that the Nintendo Switch™ 2 version of Borderlands® 4 is available for pre-order. The game will launch on October 3, 2025. Borderlands 4 is the next installment in the critically and commercially-successful franchise, and the Nintendo Switch™ 2 System allows players to experience all the mayhem of the looter-shooter on the go.
